Seems that newer SDK levels require a default constructor: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/29762949/error-this-fragment-should-provide-a-default-constructor-a-public-constructor

You can try adding a default constructor (or just lower your target API level)l. Feel free to send a PR with the fix if this addresses the issue for you, thanks.
